{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"4000000000000001","type":"group","x":0,"y":1000,"width":1860,"height":620,"color":"3","label":"データフロー (人 ↔ ロボット, ローカル STT/TTS)"},
		{"id":"1000000000000001","type":"group","x":0,"y":0,"width":1860,"height":360,"color":"3","label":"Composition (autoconnect)"},
		{"id":"2000000000000001","type":"group","x":0,"y":400,"width":920,"height":580,"color":"3","label":"_common_agentic_ja の中身"},
		{"id":"3000000000000001","type":"group","x":940,"y":400,"width":920,"height":580,"color":"3","label":"unitree_go2_spatial_bounded の中身"},
		{"id":"0000000000000001","type":"text","text":"# unitree-go2-agentic-local-tts  構成図","x":20,"y":-90,"width":760,"height":50},
		{"id":"1000000000000002","type":"text","text":"**unitree_go2_agentic_local_tts**  (autoconnect)\n\nLLM = `TimedMcpClient(model=$DIMOS_LLM_MODEL, system_prompt=SYSTEM_PROMPT_JA)`  ·  既定 `gpt-4o`  ·  `.disabled_modules(SecurityModule)`","x":40,"y":40,"width":1780,"height":110,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"1000000000000003","type":"text","text":"**unitree_go2_spatial_bounded**\n\nロボット基盤 + 知覚 + 地図 (bounded 版)","x":40,"y":180,"width":410,"height":150,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"1000000000000004","type":"text","text":"**McpServer**\n\nスキルを MCP ツールとして公開","x":480,"y":180,"width":410,"height":150,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"1000000000000005","type":"text","text":"**★ TimedMcpClient (LLM)**\n\n`model = $DIMOS_LLM_MODEL` (既定 `gpt-4o`)\n`system_prompt = SYSTEM_PROMPT_JA`","x":920,"y":180,"width":410,"height":150,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"1000000000000006","type":"text","text":"**_common_agentic_ja**\n\nJA スキル束 + PTT ローカルマイク + TTS","x":1360,"y":180,"width":410,"height":150,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"2000000000000002","type":"text","text":"NavigationSkillContainer","x":40,"y":450,"width":840,"height":50,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"2000000000000003","type":"text","text":"PersonFollowSkillContainer  (camera_info = GO2Connection)","x":40,"y":510,"width":840,"height":50,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"2000000000000004","type":"text","text":"UnitreeSkillContainer","x":40,"y":570,"width":840,"height":50,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"2000000000000005","type":"text","text":"**★ PttKeyboard**\n\npynput global hotkey  ·  既定 `F9` (`$DIMOS_PTT_KEY` で変更可)\n押下中だけ `mic_gate=True` を publish","x":40,"y":630,"width":840,"height":80,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"2000000000000006","type":"text","text":"**★ LocalMicrophoneJa**\n\nPortAudio mic  ·  `mic_gate=True` の間だけ PCM を buffer\n立下りで一発話を `mic_utterance` (AudioEvent) として publish","x":40,"y":720,"width":840,"height":80,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"2000000000000007","type":"text","text":"**★ WhisperHumanInputJa**\n\n`mic_utterance` を Whisper にかけ `/human_input` にテキスト投入\n`$DIMOS_WHISPER_MODEL` (既定 `base`)  ·  `$DIMOS_WHISPER_FP16=1` で FP16","x":40,"y":810,"width":840,"height":80,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"2000000000000009","type":"text","text":"**★ AssistantSpeechNodeJa**\n\n`agent: In[BaseMessage]` を購読し `AIMessage.content` を直接\n`OpenJTalkTTSNode` → `SounddeviceAudioOutput` (48 kHz) に流す\n(speak ツールは廃止 → system prompt からも除外)","x":40,"y":900,"width":840,"height":70,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"3000000000000002","type":"text","text":"**unitree_go2**  (basic + mapping + nav planners + MovementManager)","x":980,"y":450,"width":840,"height":60,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"3000000000000003","type":"text","text":"SpatialMemory","x":980,"y":520,"width":840,"height":50,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"3000000000000004","type":"text","text":"PerceiveLoopSkill","x":980,"y":580,"width":840,"height":50,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"3000000000000005","type":"text","text":"SecurityModule  ※ `.disabled_modules(SecurityModule)` で無効化\n(SpeakSkillSpec satisfier を要求するが local-tts では SpeakSkill を置かないため)","x":980,"y":640,"width":840,"height":80,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"3000000000000006","type":"text","text":"GO2Connection  (WebRTC)","x":980,"y":730,"width":840,"height":60,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"4000000000000010","type":"text","text":"[ユーザー音声]","x":40,"y":1060,"width":160,"height":70,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"4000000000000011","type":"text","text":"**LocalMicrophoneJa**\n(PortAudio, PCM)","x":220,"y":1060,"width":240,"height":80,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4000000000000012","type":"text","text":"**WhisperHumanInputJa**\n`language='ja'`\n`$DIMOS_WHISPER_MODEL` / `_FP16`","x":480,"y":1060,"width":260,"height":90,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4000000000000014","type":"text","text":"pLCMTransport\n`/human_input`","x":760,"y":1060,"width":220,"height":80,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"4000000000000015","type":"text","text":"**TimedMcpClient (LLM)**\n`SYSTEM_PROMPT_JA`","x":1000,"y":1060,"width":240,"height":80,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4000000000000016","type":"text","text":"**McpServer**","x":1260,"y":1060,"width":160,"height":80,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"4000000000000017","type":"text","text":"Navigation / PersonFollow /\nUnitree skills","x":1440,"y":1060,"width":240,"height":80,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"4000000000000018","type":"text","text":"MovementManager →\nGO2Connection → 犬","x":1700,"y":1060,"width":140,"height":80,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"4000000000000020","type":"text","text":"**PttKeyboard**\n`F9` 押下中 = True","x":220,"y":1180,"width":240,"height":70,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4000000000000040","type":"text","text":"**WebUI なし**: マイク入力は PTT ローカルマイクのみ。WebUI の `web_audio` 経路は本 blueprint では未配線。","x":480,"y":1180,"width":960,"height":70,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"4000000000000030","type":"text","text":"**TimedMcpClient.agent**\n→ `BaseMessage` stream","x":1000,"y":1280,"width":260,"height":80,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4000000000000031","type":"text","text":"**AssistantSpeechNodeJa**\n`AIMessage.content` → text","x":740,"y":1280,"width":240,"height":80,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4000000000000032","type":"text","text":"**OpenJTalkTTSNode**\n(JA pyopenjtalk)","x":480,"y":1280,"width":240,"height":80,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4000000000000033","type":"text","text":"**SounddeviceAudioOutput**\n(48 kHz)","x":220,"y":1280,"width":240,"height":80,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4000000000000034","type":"text","text":"[スピーカー]","x":40,"y":1280,"width":160,"height":80,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"5000000000000001","type":"text","text":"**凡例**  ·  紫=合成ルート  ·  シアン=upstream モジュール  ·  オレンジ=★ local-tts 差分  ·  緑=データフロー / ロボット制御  ·  赤=無効化 / 非配線\n\n**local-tts が upstream agentic と異なる主な点**:  \n1) STT: `WhisperHumanInputJa(language='ja')` をローカル実行 (`$DIMOS_WHISPER_MODEL` / `$DIMOS_WHISPER_FP16` で切替)  \n2) マイク入力: WebUI を捨て `LocalMicrophoneJa` + `PttKeyboard` (F9 押下中だけ録音 → 立下りで一発話を `mic_utterance` に publish)  \n3) LLM: `TimedMcpClient` (`$DIMOS_LLM_MODEL`, 既定 `gpt-4o`) + `SYSTEM_PROMPT_JA`  \n4) TTS: `AssistantSpeechNodeJa` が `McpClient.agent` の `AIMessage` を直接 `OpenJTalkTTSNode` → `SounddeviceAudioOutput` に流す (speak ツール経由ではなく LLM 応答テキストをそのまま発話)  \n5) `SecurityModule` は `.disabled_modules` で無効化 (SpeakSkill を置かないため SpeakSkillSpec satisfier が成立しない)  \n6) PTT キーは `$DIMOS_PTT_KEY` で変更可 (既定 `F9`)","x":0,"y":1620,"width":1860,"height":300,"color":"3"}
	],
